Installation Instructions
*************************

These are basic installation instructions assuming you have administrator rights.

As of version 0.1 the following OS are supported:
- OS X,
- Linux,
- Windows has not yet been tested.

In order to install the package 'RcppGO', use either one of these methods. 

# Method 1
devtools::install_github("peterkehlerjr/RcppGO")

# Method 2
install.packages("remotes")
remotes::install_github("peterkehlerjr/RcppGO")

# Method 3
library(githubinstall)
githubinstall("peterkehlerjr/RcppGO")

# Method 4 
download the package from github, cd to the package directory and in the terminal use
R CMD build RcppGO
R CMD INSTALL RcppGO

You can get support and report bugs under:
peter.kehler.jr@googlemail.com
